snippet.title: Gorathar - A Strategy-filled Roguelite Deckbuilder Adventure (Trailer)
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2545950/Gorathar/

Download now -
iOS - https://apps.apple.com/us/app/gorathar/id1667644719
Android - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.GuayabaGames.Gorathar

Embark on an unforgettable adventure with Gorathar, a rogue-lite deckbuilder game with a unique mechanic. You can use your cards on your turn, or save them in your pocket for later!
